headline: Intuit Expands AI Tax And Hiring Platform With TurboTax Stores And Checkr
summary: Intuit has opened a new flagship TurboTax store in New York City, expanding its in person support for tax filers. The company is rolling out nearly 600 AI powered tax expert locations and 20 new TurboTax stores across the US. Intuit has also partnered with Checkr to integrate background checks into QuickBooks Online Payroll and Intuit Enterprise Suite. headline: Intuit Launches New Career Pipeline Program to Empower the Next Generation of Accountants in the AI Era
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., January 28, 2026--Intuit (NASDAQ: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, announced today its new Career Pipeline Program, committing to upskilling one million students in the accounting industry over the next five years.
